{"tid":1185599,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【義舉】佩雷斯撫養雷耶斯兒子 將他帶到皇馬","createTime":"2019-06-04T10:58:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T11:11:58.000Z","uid":52571,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"64701e877c7cd771f8d449998d5bc2be7c971dd1","tid":1185599,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T10:58:12.000Z","msg":"知名的「反皇馬人士」克里斯托瓦爾-索里亞在西班牙節目El Chiringuito透露，皇馬主席佩雷斯（F.Perez）將撫養雷耶斯的兒子小雷耶斯（J.Reyes Lopez）。<br />\n<br />\n  他說：「我不知道在這裡說好不好，但是我想告訴大家，昨天佩雷斯主席真的很偉大。大家知道我對於皇馬的立場，但是這件事和足球無關：佩雷斯主席告訴我，他會幫助撫養和照顧雷耶斯11歲的大兒子。我知道這個孩子下個賽季要去皇馬踢球了。」<br />\n<br />\n  「佩雷斯主席很感人，昨天在雷耶斯的葬禮上，他告訴我：<span style=\"color: red;\">只要我還在，就不讓這個孩子在18歲之前受任何的苦。</span>」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n  據西班牙媒體的消息，雷耶斯的兒子小雷耶斯，即將告別雷加利斯青訓，前往皇馬青訓營踢球。"},{"pid":"884e6ade8f5ee6fdea3c72ed13112e03fd0d3735","tid":1185599,"uid":60658,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T10:58:52.000Z","msg":"「佩雷斯主席很肉酸。」"},{"pid":"215c77a6b610558194fda4e633ff0c0b45f1da87","tid":1185599,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"884e6ade8f5ee6fdea3c72ed13112e03fd0d3735","tid":1185599,"uid":60658,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T10:58:52.000Z","msg":"「佩雷斯主席很肉酸。」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T10:59:46.000Z","msg":"師兄有冇喊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d56af7d9f91ac3849214ba474417d98d50de5fb9","tid":1185599,"uid":60658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"215c77a6b610558194fda4e633ff0c0b45f1da87","tid":1185599,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"884e6ade8f5ee6fdea3c72ed13112e03fd0d3735","tid":1185599,"uid":60658,"like":7,"dislike":0,"sc